title: Episode 139 w/ Ja Rule

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episodes the guys drink it up with Ja Rule. The guys cover a lot of topics from Fat Joe trying to being 50 Cent and him out on stage together, to JLO, to topics ranging from before Def Jam up until now!
